OL,3,CTwo teenagers charged with murder of
OL,4,C'loving father' in Barry
OL,6,FTwo teenagers have been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder following the death of a man in
OL,8,FBarry.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Barry Road in
OL,11,FBarry just before midnight on Monday,
OL,12,FJune 30 to reports of a stabbing.
OL,14,FA 38-year-old man named by South Wales
OL,15,FPolice as Kamran Aman died after the
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,FTwo boys, aged 16 and 17, from
OL,19,FLlantwit Major, who cannot be named
OL,20,Ffor legal reasons, have both been
OL,21,Fcharged with murder.
