OL,3,CTwo teenagers charged with murder of
OL,4,C'loving father' in Barry
OL,6,FThey are due to appear at Cardiff
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday, July
OL,8,F3. Detectives say they are not looking
OL,9,Ffor anyone else in connection with
OL,10,FKamran's death.
OL,12,FIn a tribute released through the
OL,13,Fforce, Kamran's family said: "It is
OL,14,Fwith profound sorrow and heavy hearts
OL,15,Fthat we mourn the tragic loss of
OL,16,FKamran. A devoted husband, a loving
OL,17,Ffather, a cherished son, brother,
OL,18,Funcle, and loyal friend, Kamran was
OL,19,Fthe heart of his family and loved
OL,20,Fwithin in his community.
