OL,6,F"Known for his, generous spirit, and
OL,7,Fkind heart, Kamran brought warmth and
OL,8,Fstrength to everyone he met. His
OL,9,Fabsence leaves an immeasurable void in
OL,10,Fthe lives of all who knew him.
OL,12,F"As we grieve this unimaginable loss,
OL,13,Fwe also honour and celebrate the life
OL,14,Fhe lived and the impact he made. May
OL,15,Fhis memory be a blessing."
