OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Mark O'Shea,
OL,7,Ffrom the South Wales Police Major
OL,8,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "Our
OL,9,Fthoughts are with Kamran's family and
OL,10,Ffriends, as they have been since the
OL,11,Ftragic events of Monday night.
OL,13,F"We would very much like to thank the
OL,14,Fcommunity for the support and
OL,15,Finformation that has already been
OL,16,Fprovided."
OL,18,FSouth Wales Police says the
OL,19,Finvestigation is continuing and anyone
OL,20,Fwith information is asked to contact
OL,21,Fthe force.
